## Breaking Changes That Apply to You

**`[ExpectedException]` removed** (lines 9, 16) — This is your main issue. The attribute no longer exists in v4. Replace with `Assert.ThrowsExactly<T>` inside the test body:

```csharp
// Before
[ExpectedException(typeof(ArgumentNullException))]
[TestMethod]
public void Validate_NullInput_ThrowsArgumentNull()
{
    Validate(null);
}

// After
[TestMethod]
public void Validate_NullInput_ThrowsArgumentNull()
{
    Assert.ThrowsExactly<ArgumentNullException>(() => Validate(null));
}
```

## Other Breaking Changes to Watch For

